* Associated deities: {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Tagiribime-no-Mikoto|1=UNKNOWN}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|qid=Q11059454|lt=Ichikishimahime-no-Mikoto|1=Ichikishima-hime}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Tagitsuhime-no-Mikoto|1=UNKNOWN}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Sarutahiko-no-Kami|1=Sarutahiko Ōkami|qid=Q3090037}}, {{ill|lt=Susanoo|Q272993|qid=Q272993|lt=Hayasusanoo-no-Mikoto|1=Susanoo-no-Mikoto}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Ame-no-Oshihomimi-no-Mikoto|1=UNKNOWN}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|qid=Q10940685|lt=Ame-no-Hohi-no-Mikoto|1=Ame no Hohi}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Amatsu-hikone-no-Mikoto|1=UNKNOWN}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Ikatsu-hikone-no-Mikoto|1=UNKNOWN}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Kumano-Kusubi-no-Mikoto|1=UNKNOWN}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|qid=Q3080728|lt=Ukanomitama-no-Mikoto|1=Ukanomitama}}, {{ill|Ōnamuchi-no-Mikoto|lt=Ōnamuchi-no-Mikoto|qid=Q276944|1=Ōkuninushi}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Ōta-no-Mikoto|1=UNKNOWN}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Ōmiya-no-Megami|1=UNKNOWN}}, {{ill|lt=Ukemochi-no-Kami|Q2280323|qid=Q2280323|1=Ukemochi}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Kotohira-no-Kami|1=UNKNOWN}}, and one unspecified seat

